---
title: Creamy Bacon & Basil Pesto Penne with Apple Salad & Parmesan
description: The only way to improve the age-old family favourite, pesto pasta, is to add some crispy bacon and sharp Parmesan.
With oh-so-many textures and well-loved flavours, this dish is sure to please the whole table!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-bacon-basil-pesto-penne-66e6d278.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/creamy-bacon-basil-pesto-penne-610cdf3b9deb5435314e2ba9-cf510df1.pdf
